Feature: Authorization    Scenario: Admins can manage all resources     Given I am logged in as an admin     When I view a resource     Then I should have management options for that resource    Scenario: Regular users cannot manage resources     Given I am logged in as a regular user     When I view a resource     Then I should not have management options for that resource        Scenario: Admins can access admin pages     Given I am logged in as an admin     When I access an admin page     Then I should be able to view the admin page    Scenario: Regular users cannot access admin pages      Given I am logged in as a regular user     When I attempt to access an admin page     Then I should see an unauthorized access error message     And I should be redirected to my dashboard